# Workspace Policy: No Worktree Flow

- Do not suggest, require, or ask about git worktrees.
- Execute all tasks in the current repository workspace unless the user explicitly requests a worktree.
- Do not block implementation on worktree setup.
- If a skill suggests worktrees, treat this project rule as higher priority and continue inline.
